description: BACK ON MARKET! Entire unit was just repainted and updated including new LED recessed light fixtures, bathroom vanity lights, and fixtures throughout! Take advantage of the opportunity to live in this expansive 3 bed, 2.5 bath townhouse located in the heart of South Boston. With a large open concept living and dining area on the main level, it makes for the perfect daily living and hosting space. The kitchen is well equipped, featuring updated appliances and ample counter space. Each bedroom offers ample space easily fitting a Queen or King sized bed. The primary bedroom on the top floor includes a large en-suite bathroom and tons of additional storage space. Added conveniences include dedicated in-unit laundry conveniently located on the second floor, and 2 Deeded garage parking spots. The unit also makes for a fantastic investment property and has historically received $4,500/mo. with the potential of $5,000 with the recent updates to the unit.
